Name: Geese And Gats
About the game: Are you ready to take on the battle gaggle? Geese and Gats is a round based survival game where the objective is to make your way through endless wave of battle geese. Variety of Weapons . Different gats for every type of player. Destructible environment . Take a break from the geese and destroy the environment. Every structure on the snowy mountain top is destructible. Single player . Relax while wading your way through armed geese with no competition. No Pay-To-Win model . There are no in-game purchases and no season pass. You get everything right out of the box.
